item.title: Translation Ready
item.dc:creator: fitness
item.content:encoded: Tested for translation readiness with other languages using PoEdit and also multilingual websites using qTranslate X plugin. Also RTL compatible.

item.title: Font Options
item.dc:creator: fitness
item.content:encoded: Tested with 600+ Google font options which allow for Cyrillic, Latin and Sub set fonts and styles as well. So write in any language you want.

item.title: Color settings
item.dc:creator: fitness
item.content:encoded: Color picker makes it easy for you to enhance and change the whole color scheme of the theme at various places to be just like you desire.

item.title: Shortcodes and Blocks
item.dc:creator: fitness
item.content:encoded: Theme comes with 30+ blocks which help in creating and setting up content easily plus it is compatible with a shortcodes plugin which allows for 100+ shortcodes to be used anywhere on the entire site. So set up your content the way you want it.

item.title: Sliders
item.dc:creator: fitness
item.content:encoded: Sliders are a way to describe things easily with visual representation and hence we tested this theme with more than 10 sliders which work flawlessly with the theme.

item.title: Header layout
item.dc:creator: fitness
item.content:encoded: Use the header you want with 4 header choices given for the homepage and add any banner or map or video for inner page banner area.

item.title: Footer layout
item.dc:creator: fitness
item.content:encoded: Footer is also given with 4 different layouts to choose from.

item.title: WooCommerce and other plugins
item.dc:creator: fitness
item.content:encoded: WooCommerce tested theme for easy shop and eCommerce as well as Contact form 7 tested for forms and NextGen gallery and other portfolio plugins tested for gallery or portfolio choices.

item.title: bbPress
item.dc:creator: fitness
item.content:encoded: Default forum from WordPress.org is also tested and is found to be compliant.

item.title: Widgets
item.dc:creator: fitness
item.content:encoded: Fully widgetized sidebars, header area and footer for easy custom widget and custom content the way you want to use them and place them. Use of dynamic Facebook Feeds and Twitter feeds and social icons and chat are among others that can be readily used.
